print("+---------- Post-Hoc Paired T-test Tests ----------+")
## [1] "+---------- Post-Hoc Paired T-test Tests ----------+"
emm1 = emmeans(dprime_mod, specs = pairwise ~ valence|age_group,
               type = 'repsonse', adjust = 'none')
emm1_fdr = emmeans(dprime_mod, specs = pairwise ~ valence|age_group,
               type = 'repsonse', adjust = 'fdr')
emm1_contrasts <- emm1$contrasts
emm1_fdr_contrasts <- emm1_fdr$contrasts
emm1_fdr_contrasts <- as.data.frame(emm1_fdr_contrasts)

emm1_contrasts <- as.data.frame(emm1_contrasts) %>% 
  mutate(p.adjust = emm1_fdr_contrasts$p.value) %>%
  separate(col = contrast, into = c('group1', 'group2'), sep = ' - ') %>%
  filter(p.value < 0.05) %>%
  mutate(sig = case_when(p.adjust < 0.05 ~ '*',
                         p.value < 0.05 ~ '#')) %>%
  add_xy_position(data = data_C, formula = dprime ~ age_group,
                  x = "age_group", group = 'valence', fun = "mean_se", dodge = 0.8)
